column2: Standard ordering expand/collapse all, expand all is always first

column3: Today I noticed that several tool windows in IntelliJ 12 Ultimate have a different ordering too: EJB, Web, JavaEE:App, Persistence, CDI
Should I create a defect in youtrack so the improvement is tracked for IntelliJ 13?

@lehnerj
It would be best if you create a YouTrack issue and mention this pull request there (and backwards).
Thanks for your reply. I created a new issue: IDEA-119065.
I just noticed that this pull request has already been merged on 04.04.2013 (git revision: fe94b55), you can close it.
Standard ordering expand/collapse all, expand all is always first
